      h1 PRIVACY POLICY ‚Äì Shelft
      p Effective Date: 01/05/2025

      p Your privacy matters to us. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your personal information when you use Shelft.

      h2 1. What Data We Collect
      p When you register, use the site, or contact us, we may collect:
      ul
        li Name and surname
        li Email address
        li Book preferences
        li Technical data like IP address, browser type, and cookies

      h2 2. How We Use Your Data
      p We use your personal data to:
      ul
        li Manage your account
        li Personalize your experience
        li Provide customer support
        li Send relevant notifications
        li Improve our services and features

      h2 3. Cookies
      p Shelft uses cookies to enhance your browsing experience and collect anonymous analytics. You may disable cookies in your browser settings.

      h2 4. Legal Basis for Processing
      p We process your data under the following legal bases:
      ul
        li Your explicit consent
        li Contractual necessity (e.g., access to features)
        li Legal obligations
        li Legitimate interests (e.g., service improvement)

      h2 5. Data Retention
      p We store your data securely and retain it while your account is active. You may request deletion at any time.

      h2 6. Data Sharing
      p We do not sell your data. We may share it only with:
      ul
        li Authentication providers (e.g., Google, if used for login)
        li Email providers (for verification and password reset)
        li Legal authorities if required by law

      h2 7. Security Measures
      p We use technical and organizational security measures to protect your data from unauthorized access or loss.

      h2 8. Your Rights
      p As a user, you have the right to:
      ul
        li Access your personal data
        li Correct inaccuracies
        li Request deletion
        li Withdraw consent
        li File a complaint with the relevant data protection authority

      h2 9. Policy Updates
      p We may update this policy occasionally. You will be informed of significant changes via the platform or email.

